Description: Sebastian is a loyal butler who moves easily from dinner parties to the underworld. Is he too good to be true? Is he even human? In this volume: children are missing and Queen Victoria is not happy.
Title: BLACK BUTLER, VOL. 7
Author: Yana Toboso

Description: 15-year-old Allen Walker roams the earth searching for "Innocence," the material used to create weapons that can destroy demons that this fictional version of 19th century England.
Title: D. GRAY-MAN, VOL. 21
Author: Katsura Hoshino

Description: Misao Harada can see into a magical realm where she is the bride demon of prophecy.
Title: BLACK BIRD, VOL. 11
Author: Kanoko Sakurakoji

Description: A Claymore - a female warrior named for her sword - stalks medieval villages to destroy Yoma, monsters who pass as humans and are difficult to kill.
Title: CLAYMORE, VOL. 19
Author: Norihiro Yagi

Description: Light Yagami discovers a supernatural notebook that allows him to murder anyone he has seen by writing their name in it. He uses this ability to try to rid the world of evil.
Title: DEATH NOTE: BLACK EDITION, VOL. 6
Author: Tsugumi Ohba

Description: Maka, an arms expert, wants to turn the Soul Eater, her living scythe, into the ultimate weapon for Death.
Title: SOUL EATER, VOL. 7
Author: Atsushi Ohkubo

Description: A mysterious disease has turned a high schoolâ€™s student body into zombies. In this volume: a zombie rampage at the airport.
Title: HIGH SCHOOL OF THE DEAD, VOL. 4
Author: Daisuke Sato and Shouji Sato
Contributor: by Daisuke Sato and Shouji Sato

Description: This series is about an incredibly positive young girl named Yotsuba. In this volume, she plays hide-and-seek with her father.
Title: YOTSUBA&!, VOL. 10
Author: Kiyohiko Azuma

Description: Life in a high school filled with werewolves and vampires continues.
Title: ROSARIO+VAMPIRE: SEASON II, VOL. 6
Author: Akihisa Ikeda

Description: Oz, who is condemned for a mysterious sin, begins to learn more about the past.
Title: PANDORA HEARTS, VOL. 7
Author: Jun Mochizuki
